Kingdom Hearts HD 2.5 ReMIX

Date      : 11-2014                   Languages: English
Platform  : PS3                       Genre    : Game

Release Info:

KINGDOM HEARTS HD 2.5 ReMIX is an HD remastered compilation of KINGDOM
HEARTS II FINAL MIX and KINGDOM HEARTS Birth by Sleep FINAL MIX. Previously
exclusive to Japan, both games will be available for the first time to North
America for the PlayStationr3 system. HD remastered cinematics from KINGDOM
HEARTS Re:coded will also be included in the compilation. The game is a
sequel to last year's KINGDOM HEARTS HD 1.5 ReMIX and will lead into the
highly anticipated KINGDOM HEARTS III.
